report.ATA.Rd

Specialized Screen Print Function of ATA model

# S3 method for ATA
report(object, ...)

Arguments

object

An estimated model.
...

Unused.

Examples

  as_tsibble(USAccDeaths) %>% model(ata = AutoATA(value ~ trend("A") + season("M"))) %>% report()
